  body
    .container-fluid
      header
        ul.nav.nav-justified
          li.logo
            a(href='#landing' data-scroll) Spacepicnic
          li
            a(href='#our-work' data-scroll) Our work
          li
            a(href='#who-are-we' data-scroll) Who are we
          li
            a(href='#we-do-talks' data-scroll) Talks
          li
            a(href='#our-process' data-scroll) Our process
          li
            a.typeform-share.link(href="https://domas.typeform.com/to/Ditaxt" data-mode="1" target="_blank")
              | Hire us

      #landing
        .container
          .text-center
            .row
              h1 How about making something breathtaking?
              h3 this design studio builds beautiful web and app experiences
              a.btn.btn-default.call(type='button' href='#our-work' data-scroll)
                | See our work

            .scroll-down.row
              a(href='#our-work' data-scroll)
                img(src='img/scroll.png')

      #our-work.text-center
        .row
          h2 Experiences we've built

          .screens
            img(src='img/screens.png')

        .built-with.container
          .row
            .col-md-offset-1.col-md-5
              | The beautiful products here were designed and built with
              | Bootstrap, Angular.js, Ember.js, React.js and Meteor.js.

        .more-works
          ul.nav.nav-justified
            a.btn.btn-default.call(type='button' href='https://dribbble.com/benasbitvinskas'  target='_blank')
              | More designs
            a.btn.btn-default.call(type='button' href='https://github.com/Nedomas/'  target='_blank')
              | Code

      #who-are-we
        .abstract.row.text-center
          h2 Who are we

        .members.row
          .member
            .container
              .col-md-offset-2.col-md-2
                img.avatar(src='img/avatar_domas.png')
              .info.col-md-6
                h3
                  a(href='http://domasbitvinskas.com' target='_blank') Domas Bitvinskas
                p
                  | A rockstar developer who is actively pushing coding to the
                  | edge by bringing futuristic tools to the present.
                p
                  | Works with Ruby on Rails for more than 3 years. Professional
                  | coder at SameSystem. Freelances on Ionic, Angular.js,
                  | React.js and Meteor js.
                p
                  | Constantly pushes his fears forward by doing all kinds of
                  | extreme sports - from skydiving to snowboarding.

            .open-source
              .container
                .col-md-offset-2.col-md-5
                  h5 Also develops Open-Souce libraries of the future
                  iframe(src="http://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=Nedomas&repo=zapata&type=watch&count=true&size=large" height="30" width="170" frameborder="0" scrolling="0" style="width:170px; height: 30px;" allowTransparency="true")
                .col-md-4
                  img(src='img/zapata.png')

          .member.container
            .col-md-offset-2.col-md-2
              img.avatar(src='img/avatar_benas.png')
            .info.col-md-6
              h3
                a(href='http://benasbitvinskas.com' target='_blank') Benas Bitvinskas
              h5 (obviously, we are brothers)
              p
                | A rising star in the design world. Willing to stand on his
                | head if this makes for a better user experience. Also digs
                | brand design and does professional design for more than a
                | year.

      #we-do-talks
        .abstract
          .row.text-center
            h2 We do talks
        .main-talks.row
          .container
          .text-center.col-md-offset-3.col-md-6
            p
              | We are active in the developer superstar community.
            p
              | Doing all kinds of talks in various developer conferences.

        .container
          .talk-slides.row
            .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
              img.slide(src='img/rockstarsandproductivity.png')
            .col-md-3
              img.slide(src='img/rubyonrailsisdead.png')
            .col-md-3
              img.slide(src='img/whydoesruby.png')

          .talk-descriptions.row
            .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
              h4
                a(href='https://speakerdeck.com/nedomas/rockstars-and-productivity')
                  | Rockstars and Productivity
              h6 at
                a(href='http://2014.rubyconf.lt')
                  |  RubyConf 2014
            .col-md-3
              h4
                a(href='https://speakerdeck.com/nedomas/ruby-on-rails-is-dead')
                  | Ruby on Rails is dead (its a joke)
              h6 at
                a(href='http://vilniusrb.lt')
                  |  VilniusRB
            .col-md-3
              h4
                a(href='https://speakerdeck.com/nedomas/why-does-ruby-own-the-startup-world')
                  | Why does Ruby own the startup world?
              h6 at
                a(href='http://hubvilnius.lt/apie/kvieciame-moksleivius-i-startcamp-vasaros-stovykla-hube')
                  |  StartCamp

          p.text-center
            a.btn.btn-default.call(type='button' href='http://domasbitvinskas.com/talks'  target='_blank')
              | More talks

      #our-process
        .abstract
          .row.text-center
            h2 Our process
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-3.col-md-offset-2
              img.process-illustration(src='img/process.png')
            .process-description.col-md-4
              p
                | We can do almost any task you can think of. From the conception
                | of an idea, to a fully fledged product thats shipped to
                | thousands of users.
              p
                | We are commited to find the best process to make the world a
                | better place in the most efficient way.

          .row.usual-process
            .col-md-offset-2
              h3 This is what we usually do

              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Make sure we understand each other
                  p
                    | Do a Google Hangout with you and discover what your secret
                    | wishes are.

              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Gather initial data
                  p
                    | Write the user stories to be as close to reality as
                    | possible.

              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Design the prototype
                  p
                    | Do this in InvisionApp and collaborate on making the user
                    | experience perfect.

              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Prototype the app
                  p
                    | Choose the best framework for the job and make a working
                    | prototype. Framework selection includes Ruby on Rails,
                    | Ionic, Angular.js, Meteor.js, React.js.

              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Do callaborated testing
                  p
                    | Improve the design on your feedback and lock it up with
                    | tests.
              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Add metrics
                  p
                    | Track every step of the user for easier future decision
                    | making. Use Segment.com, Mixpanel and Google Analytics.
              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Ship it
                  p
                    | Select the best hosting solution for the job. Choose between
                    | Heroku and a VPS.
              .step.row
                .bubble.col-md-1.text-center.vcenter
                  img(src='img/bubble.png')
                .col-md-6
                  h4 Analyze
                  p
                    | Use the data from metrics to improve the designs and get the
                    | last percents of the conversion rate.

      footer
        .container.text-center
          h2 Enough, enough. Let's start hitting it hard together
          a.btn.btn-default.call.typeform-share.link(href="https://domas.typeform.com/to/Ditaxt" data-mode="1" target="_blank")
            | Hire us
